<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[الضُّوْء]</span>: لغةٌ في الضَّوء.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فُعْلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
